    "energies= data['Energy']\n",
    "danceabilities=data['Danceability']\n",
    "valences=data['Valence']\n",
    "NO_CLUSTERS=3\n",
    "\n",
    "# Combine the lists into a single 2D array\n",
    "features = np.array(list(zip(energies, danceabilities, valences)))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Apply K-Means clustering\n",
    "# TODO: Fine-tune, maybe make it more robust\n",
    "# kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=NO_CLUSTERS, init=[[0.4798,     0.6302,     0.75104   ],\n",
    "#                                     [0.82407143, 0.55757143, 0.75971429],\n",
    "#                                     [0.2183,     0.493,      0.34005263],\n",
    "#                                     [0.51176471, 0.48335294, 0.38403529],\n",
    "#                                     [0.862,      0.39761538, 0.34144615]],random_state=42)\n",
    "\n",
    "kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=NO_CLUSTERS, init=[ [1, 0, 1],\n",
    "                                              # [0.5,0.5,0.5],\n",
    "                                    [0,     0,      0],\n",
    "                                    [0.5, 1, 1]],random_state=42)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "kmeans.fit(features)\n",
    "labels = kmeans.labels_\n",
    "centroids = kmeans.cluster_centers_\n",
    "\n",
    "# Calculate distances to centroids\n",
    "distances = cdist(features, centroids, metric='euclidean')  # Shape: (n_samples, n_clusters)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Convert distances to fuzzy membership scores\n",
    "# Using a Gaussian kernel\n",
    "sigma = distances.std()  # Or tune this manually\n",
    "fuzzy_memberships = np.exp(-distances**2 / (2 * sigma**2))\n",
    "fuzzy_memberships /= fuzzy_memberships.sum(axis=1, keepdims=True)  # Normalize\n",
    "\n",
    "max_memberships=np.max(fuzzy_memberships, axis=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "labels_fuzzy=np.argmax(fuzzy_memberships, axis=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "data[\"Label\"]=labels_fuzzy\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "#generate normal surface\n",
    "center_mean=np.mean(features, axis=0, keepdims=True)\n",
    "svd=np.linalg.svd(features.transpose() - center_mean.transpose())\n",
    "\n",
    "left= svd[0]\n",
    "\n",
    "normal=left[:,-1]\n",
    "\n",
    "d_plane=-center_mean.dot(normal)\n",
    "\n",
    "# create x,y\n",
    "xx, yy = np.meshgrid(np.arange(0,1,0.1), np.arange(0,1,0.1))\n",
    "# and z\n",
    "zz = (-normal[0] * xx - normal[1] * yy - d_plane) * 1. /normal[2]\n",
    "\n",
    "# add projection, need the grad, and a point on each axes\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))\n",
    "ax = fig.add_subplot(111, projection='3d')\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "check=data.loc[data[\"Track Name\"]==\"Blood Upon Stone\"]\n",
    "\n",
    "# Plotting the points, colored by cluster labels\n",
    "scatter = ax.scatter(features[:, 0], features[:, 1], features[:, 2], c=labels_fuzzy, cmap='viridis', s=max_memberships * 100, alpha=max_memberships)\n",
    "scatterc=ax.scatter(centroids[:, 0], centroids[:, 1], centroids[:, 2],c='red', s=100, marker='x', alpha=1) \n",
    "\n",
    "#plot normal plane\n",
    "plane= ax.plot_surface(xx, yy, zz, alpha=0.2)\n",
    "\n",
    "# plot gradient projection\n",
    "\n",
    "n_z=np.array([-normal[1]/2,normal[0]/2,0])\n",
    "c_z=np.array([center_mean[0][0],center_mean[0][1],0])\n",
    "point1=c_z-n_z\n",
    "point2=c_z+n_z\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.plot([point1[0], point2[0]],[point1[1], point2[1]],[point1[2], point2[2]])\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "n_y=[-normal[2],0,normal[0]]\n",
    "c_y=np.array([center_mean[0][0],1,center_mean[0][2]])\n",
    "point1=c_y-n_y\n",
    "point2=c_y+n_y\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.plot([point1[0], point2[0]],[point1[1], point2[1]],[point1[2], point2[2]])\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "n_x=[0,-normal[2]/2,normal[1]/2]\n",
    "c_x=np.array([0,center_mean[0][1],center_mean[0][2]])\n",
    "point1=c_x-n_x\n",
    "point2=c_x+n_x\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.plot([point1[0], point2[0]],[point1[1], point2[1]],[point1[2], point2[2]])\n",
    "\n",
    "# for idx in range(3):\n",
    "#     n_idx=np.concatenate((normal[:idx],normal[idx+1:]))\n",
    "#     grad=-n_idx[0]/n_idx[1]\n",
    "#     ax.plot(grad)\n",
    "\n",
    "for idx, xyz in enumerate(centroids):\n",
    "    ax.text(xyz[0],xyz[1]+0.02,xyz[2]-0.05, str(idx), size='xx-large')\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "# Adding labels and title\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel('Energy')\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel('Danceability')\n",
    "ax.set_zlabel('Valence')\n",
    "ax.set_title('3D Scatter Plot of Songs')\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.set_xlim([0, 1])\n",
    "ax.set_ylim([0, 1])\n",
    "ax.set_zlim([0, 1])\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "# Show the plot\n",
